{"tid":839262,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩球會/國家隊章大家覺得靚？","createTime":"2018-09-27T21:07:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-30T05:46:58.000Z","uid":210794,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"0d136436d634a2c2e553c99c33ba2e7e177c993f","tid":839262,"uid":210794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T21:07:56.000Z","msg":"純粹講個章，咩隊都冇所謂。最好可以講吓點解。<br />\n拋磚：<br />\n球會：利華古遜、法蘭克福、科隆、恩高斯達特、曼城（舊章）、利物浦、紐卡素、海倫芬<br />\n國家隊：德國、奧地利、荷蘭、日本、俄羅斯、捷克<br />\n自己鍾意有歐洲紋章元素、同埋有啲地方象徵嘅章（好似啲鷹、獅子咁）。"},{"pid":"fc7eb8b65e323d90f4c980f7263d68f31093a034","tid":839262,"uid":150400,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T21:08:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3ac83835124f09744cd8ff1e7e84a9cc88e4414d","tid":839262,"uid":41093,"like":1,"dislike":23,"score":-22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T21:42:52.000Z","msg":"中國香港"},{"pid":"fd6bcbbb6db7d877951e92846fae1eb7f61f75d0","tid":839262,"uid":36238,"like":3,"dislike":113,"score":-110,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T21:49:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/thumb/7/7a/Manchester_United_FC_crest.svg/1200px-Manchester_United_FC_crest.svg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fthumb%2F7%2F7a%2FManchester_United_FC_crest.svg%2F1200px-Manchester_United_FC_crest.svg.png&h=b46bfff5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e26f972aa89493d7748a7dc2dce34f4d01727cf7","tid":839262,"uid":149852,"like":24,"dislike":5,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T22:27:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/28/062719_58e3dc3120c5d8a7f873f8b76bd48663.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F28%2F062719_58e3dc3120c5d8a7f873f8b76bd48663.png&h=3cc35a03&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"994869bab4e272b52fb880031b22cdc4c01d7c30","tid":839262,"uid":210794,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"fc7eb8b65e323d90f4c98